        Help keep our community thriving! Your support helps cover server costs and
        enables us to continue providing a great Minecraft experience.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Coming Soon Section -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
